data.text:
STOP EXOTIC PESTS

Citizen reports of exotic pests help can mean the difference between eradiction and epidemic. Report pests that are damaging any of your plants!

Read More

SUCCESS STORY

The Giant African Land Snail harbors human parasites and damages crops and structures. Florida has been working since 2011 to eradicate this pest.

Learn More
